  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="856" ind1="4" ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="u">http://inspirehep.net/record/1299121/files/yield2.png</subfield>
    <subfield code="y">00004 Differential $\gamma$-ray energy spectra per annihilation  for a fixed annihilation channel (b bar) and for a few sample values of WIMP masses \cite{dark}. For comparison we also show the emissivity, with an arbitrarily rescaled normalization, from the interaction of primaries with the interstellar medium.  The solid lines are the total yields, while the dashed lines are components not due to $\pi^0$ decays.</subfield>
